DescDetail: <<
  Cextra is a program for downloading and converting an arbitrary eText by
  http://www.zeno.org or http://gutenberg.spiegel.de/ to a clean and valid
  XHTML-file which can be used as source for ebook conversion tools like
  Calibre.
<<

DescUsage: <<
Usage: cextra options
	--author -a value : Author
	[--debug -d] : Enable debugging output
	[--help -h] : display help
	--profile -f /(zeno|gb_de|default)/ : Extraction profile to be used.
	--publisher -p value : Publisher
	--subTitle -s value : Subtitle
	--target -o value : Target output directory (*** mandatory ***)
	--title -t value : Title
	--url -u value : URL of the source webpage  (*** mandatory ***)

Use java -jar cextra.jar -h to get a full list of options
<<

